@page "/CountTrackula"

<PageTitle>CountTrackula - Fish Sauce Games</PageTitle>

<section class="project-hero">
    <div class="project-text">
        <h1>CountTrackula</h1>
        <p><!-- Add your CountTrackula description here --></p>
        <a href="/CountTrackula/App" class="btn-primary">Launch App</a>
    </div>
    <div class="project-media">
        <!-- Drop your CountTrackula image or gif here: wwwroot/images/counttrackula-hero.gif -->
        <img src="images/CountTrackula.png" alt="CountTrackula app" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
    </div>
</section>

<section class="track-everything">
    <h2>Track everything!</h2>
    <p>Use Count Trackula to track anything and everything.</p>  
    <p>Want to get into journalling?  CountTrackula! </p>
    <p>Want to track your macros?  CountTrackula! </p>
    <p>How about Workouts?  CountTrackula!</p>
    <p>This app was built to track fitness, nutrition, habit, and health markers.
        Easily export to json for consumption by an LLM of your choice (They all read Json)
    </p>
    <p>
        This app integrates with your google drive so it can synchronize between devices.
        Install it on your phone, use it on your desktop, supports offline and manual sync as well.
    </p>
    
</section>
